                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "API Referentie",
                        "level": 1
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 3,
                        "content": "Integreer IntraVox met externe systemen via onze RESTful API. Alle endpoints zijn beschikbaar via de Nextcloud OCS API."
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 2,
                "backgroundColor": "",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "content": "Authenticatie",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "Alle API calls vereisen authenticatie via:\n\n**Basic Auth:**\n```\nAuthorization: Basic base64(username:password)\n```\n\n**App Password:**\n```\nAuthorization: Basic base64(username:app_password)\n```"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 2,
                        "order": 1,
                        "content": "Base URL",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 2,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "Alle endpoints gebruiken deze basis URL:\n\n```\nhttps://your-nextcloud.com/ocs/v2.php/apps/intravox/api/v1\n```\n\n**Headers:**\n```\nOCS-APIRequest: true\nContent-Type: application/json\n```"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "divider",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "style": "solid",
                        "color": "",
                        "height": "2px"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "var(--color-background-hover)",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "content": "Pages Endpoints",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "| Method | Endpoint | Beschrijving |\n|--------|----------|-------------|\n| GET | /pages | Lijst alle pagina's |\n| GET | /pages/{id} | Haal specifieke pagina op |\n| POST | /pages | Maak nieuwe pagina |\n| PUT | /pages/{id} | Update bestaande pagina |\n| DELETE | /pages/{id} | Verwijder pagina |"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "content": "Voorbeeld: Pagina Ophalen",
                        "level": 3
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "```bash\ncurl -X GET \\\n  https://cloud.example.com/ocs/v2.php/apps/intravox/api/v1/pages/home \\\n  -H 'OCS-APIRequest: true' \\\n  -H 'Authorization: Basic dXNlcjpwYXNz'\n```\n\n**Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"ocs\": {\n    \"data\": {\n      \"uniqueId\": \"page-abc123\",\n      \"title\": \"Homepage\",\n      \"layout\": { ... }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "var(--color-background-hover)",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "content": "Navigation Endpoints",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "| Method | Endpoint | Beschrijving |\n|--------|----------|-------------|\n| GET | /navigation | Haal navigatie op |\n| PUT | /navigation | Update navigatie |\n| GET | /navigation/footer | Haal footer op |\n| PUT | /navigation/footer | Update footer |"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "content": "Rate Limiting",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "De API heeft de volgende limieten:\n\n- **100 requests per minuut** per gebruiker\n- **1000 requests per uur** per IP\n\nBij overschrijding ontvangt u HTTP 429 (Too Many Requests)."
                    }
                ]
            },
